user_shibboleth
===============

An ownCloud authentication app relying on the Shibboleth Service Provider.

//This is work in progress and relies on an appropriately configured LDAP user backend.






<Location /owncloud>
    AuthType shibboleth
    Require shibboleth
    ShibUseHeaders On
    RewriteRule ^apps/user_shibboleth/login.php - [L]
</Location>

